column5: Does anyone have any info on ice conditions at dunville as of today.Would like to head out on monday.
fishmaster is gonna check today and post it... give him a call and he'll let ya know how it is. 905 701 6874

Steve said to wait a cold day or 2 he doesnt recommend it right now. Some spots had 4 inches and right beside that the spud went through according to his website. So I think I shall wait till Thursday morning if it works out.
